tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,
review: Dr Das is very friendly and efficient. She explained the problem very well and treat patients excellent.

I had multiple sitting with the Dr. Suchismita and all my sittings were rather nice. She made you feel comfortable by explaining the issue and how to fix the issue. I would say she made me and my wife decide that we get all my root canals, cavity fillings done here. She is rather experienced *** ******* at what she does, which gives you the feeling all is going to be fine.

Dr Suchi is a very friendly and patient doctor. She listens to me patiently and answers all questions without trying to stop me from asking questions. A patient always has n number of questions and wants answers for most of them from a doctor. Dr Suchi is a dental doctor who would never upset you really.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,
review: Very systematic, very prompt and understanding. Caring attitude of the doctor attending to the procedure made all the difference. Good to have visited the doctor.

Dr. Suchi was incredible at my kids dental examination and treatment. I would't hesitate to recommend her services especially in children where Dr. Suchi is very skilful in handling younger patients. Thanks JOEL
Excellent. She was meticulous in cleaning all the teeth one by one. She clearly explained the process and was able to answer all the questions
Excellent and very cooperative and the best doctor to handle kids. She is a blessed dental doctor for my kid.
Polite humble to patient and the service is fast . The Dental tretment was gentle and no after effects
Dr Suchi was very thorough in explaining the problems and the diagnosis plan. She was also very goodbye putting me at ease while performing the procedure.
